## Implementation Requirements
* Keep the analytics layer completely decoupled from business logic.
* Ensure adding or removing an analytics provider requires minimal configuration changes.
* Prioritize privacy by collecting only anonymous metadata.
* Minimize impact on performance using lazy loading, deferred initialization, batching, and non-blocking event dispatch.
* Design the system to scale as phung.work grows from dozens to hundreds of tools while maintaining consistent event naming and high data quality.